crowdsourced_ai_results.analysis:
The script performs the following actions:

- Deletes all system state backups.
- Deletes all backups.
- Deletes all shadow copies.
- Disables the ability to create shadow copies.
- Sets the boot status policy to ignore all failures.
- Lists all shadow copies.
- Stops the wbadmin service.
- Deletes all system state backups.
- Deletes the backup catalog.
- Disables the wbadmin service.
- Sets the boot status policy to ignore all failures.
- Creates a batch file that deletes all shadow copies.
- Executes the batch file.
- Deletes the batch file.
- Pauses the execution of the script.
- Deletes the script itself.
